HEADWORD: Trichotomy
<hw>Tri*chot"o*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>tri`cha</grk> threefold, in three parts + <grk>te`mnein</grk> to
